snippet.title: Paw Bois (GMTK Jam 2021) | Gameplay
snippet.description:
Play the game in your browser: https://oldbomb.itch.io/pawbois

Actually this was the first time I beat the game on my own, although I wrote the code for it :D
It took me 7 minutes, can you beat me?

TEAM:
Art    Linn Spilker https://www.instagram.com/linn_tonic/
Game Design    Johanna Wulf http://johannawulf.de/
Game Design    Nina Nergadze https://www.instagram.com/ninanergadze/
Level Design    Pat https://itch.io/profile/excubitrix
Sound & Music    Jill Gibson https://fuchsfurz.itch.io/
Programming    Seb Heinrich https://twitter.com/oldb0mb
